---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Author" description="About Me">
  <section class="about">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <div class="profile">
      <div class="avatar">
        <img src="/images/avatar.jpg" alt="Profile" />
      </div>
      <div class="info">
        <h2>郭正浩</h2>
        <p class="bio">
          我是郭正浩，一名专注于实时互动与沉浸式体验开发的程序员。My name is Guo Zhenghao.  I am a programmer specializing in real-time interaction and immersive experience development.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="details">
      <h3>Background</h3>
      <p>
        毕业于广东工业大学，具备扎实的C++/C#编程基础，熟悉虚幻引擎与Unity的双引擎工作流，尤其对Gameplay框架和网络同步有深入的项目实践。I graduated from Guangdong University of Technology .I have a solid foundation in C++/C# programming and am familiar with the dual-engine workflow of Unreal Engine and Unity. I have in-depth project experience in the Gameplay framework and network synchronization.
      </p>

      <h3>Connect</h3>
      <ul class="social-links">
        <li><a href="https://github.com/UE5Gzh" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://space.bilibili.com/434410489?spm_id_from=333.33.0.0" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Bilibili</a></li>
        <li><a href="mailto:gzh2024263514@gmail.com">Email</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .profile {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
    padding: var(--space-6);
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .avatar {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .avatar img {
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border: 3px solid var(--accent);
  }

  .info h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .bio {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .details h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-top: var(--space-6);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .details p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .social-links {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .social-links a {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-4);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .social-links a:hover {
    color: var(--accent);
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .profile {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .about h1 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }
  }
</style>
